quran[53]{c,v,t}:
  51,31,"(Abrahama) a re: “Ke eng seo le tlileng ka sona lona Baromuoa ba Allah?”"
  51,32,Ba re“Re romeletsoe ho batho ba qoetseng sebeng; –
  51,33,“Ho tla ba romella lehlohlojane la lenyeta
  51,34,“E le sesupo se tsoang ho Mong`a hau ho ba tlolang meeli.”
  51,35,Ra pholosa ba-kholoang ba neng ba le teng moo
  51,36,Empa Re ile Ra fumana lelapa le le leng feela la ba inehetseng ho Allah
  51,37,Eaba Re ba siea le sesupo molemong oaba ts’abang Kahlolo e Mahlonoko
  51,38,"Le ho Moshe ho teng sesupo, Re ile Ra mo romella ho Faro ka bopaki bo totobetseng"
  51,39,"Empa Faro o ile a furalla le Matona a hae, a re: “Moloi, kapa lehlanya.”"
  51,40,"Kahoo, Re ile Ra mo nka hammoho le lebotho la hae, eaba Re ba khamisa leoatle, hobane o ne a fosahetse"
  51,41,"Le ho morabe oa Ba–A’d ho teng sesupo, Re ile Ra romella leholi’atsana kahlanong le bona"
  51,42,"Le sa kang la siea letho moo le fetileng teng, lintho tsohle li ile tsa fetoha lesupi"
  51,43,"Le ho Ba-Thamud ho teng sesupo, Bonang ba ile ba bolelloa, “Natefeloang ha nakoana!”"
  51,44,"Empa ba ile ba eba khahlanong le molao oa Mong`a bona ka tello: eaba ba nanoloa ke ho reketla ho lumang ba sa ntse ba shebile"
  51,45,Hoo ba sitiloeng le ho ema (ka maoto) kapa ho ithusa ka bo- bona
  51,46,"Joaloka batho ba habo Nooe pele ho bona: Hobane ba ile ba tlola meeli hampe"
  51,47,"Re ahile Leholimo ka Matla le Tsebo, Hobane ke Rona ba hlotseng bophara ba leholimo"
  51,48,"Ebile Re alile lefats’e: Re le ala ka makhethe ha kakang"
  51,49,"Re hlotse lintho tsohle ka bobeli, hore le tle le amohele taelo"
  51,50,"Potlakelang ho Allah ke hona: Ke molemosi ea hlakileng ho lona ea tsoang ho Allah"
  51,51,"Le se iketsetse molingoana ofe, kapa ofe papisong le Allah: Ke molemosi ea hlakileng ho lona ea tsoang ho Eena"
  51,52,"Joaloka ha ho se moromuoa ofe, kapa ofe ea kileng a tla ho Batho pele ho bona e be ha ba re: “Ke moloi, kapa lehlanya!”"
  51,53,"Na ke moetlo oo ba o neheletsaneng? Che, ke batho ba tlolang meeli eohle"
  51,54,"Ba furalle: uena ha u na molato"
  51,55,"Empa ruta (Molaetsa oa hae): hobane thuto e molemo ho Ba- kholoang"
  51,56,Ke hlotse tse sa bonoeng (li-jinn) le batho molemong oa hore ba Nts’ebeletse
  51,57,"Ha ho leo ke le kopang ho bona: kapa ho hloka phepo ho bona"
  51,58,"Hobane Ke Allah Ea fanang ka bophelo, Mong`a Ts’episo, Ea sa Thekeseleng"
  51,59,"Hobane beatsalibe karolo ea bona e ts’oana le karolo ea mehahabo bona (ea meloko ea pele): kahoo, ba se Nkope ho potlakissa (karolo eo)"
  51,60,"Sekhobo se be holim’a mahana-tumelo, boikarabellong ba Letsatsi la bona leo ba le ts’episitsoeng"
  52,1,Ka leralla (le Ts’enolo)
  52,2,Ka Molao o Ngoliloeng
  52,3,Holim’a letlalo le manolotsoeng
  52,4,Ka ntlo e chakeloang mehla eohle
  52,5,Ka Sekhele Se Phahamiselitsoeng Holimo-limo
  52,6,Le ka Leoatle le tletseng
  52,7,Ruri! Kahlolo ea Mong`a hau e tla phethahatsoa
  52,8,"Ha ho mang, kapa mang ea ka e thibelang"
  52,9,Letsatsi leo ka lona leholimo le tlang ho sisinyeha ha mpe
  52,10,Lithaba li tlang ho fofela mona le mane
  52,11,Sekhobo letsatsing leo se be holim’a bohle ba nkang ‘nete e le leshano
  52,12,Ba har’a bosaoana ba leshano
  52,13,"Letsatsi leo ba tla sutuletsoa ka har’a lihele, ho se khanyetso"
  52,14,"“Ona”, ho tla thoe: “Ke mollo, – oo le neng le tloaetse ho o hana"
  52,15,"“Na ke mafeela, kapa ebe ha le bone"
  52,16,"“Chesoang ka teng, ho ea ts’oana hore le ea o mamella kapa che: le mpa le amohela moputso oa liketso tsa lona.”"
  52,17,"Ruri! ba topileng ts’ebeletsong ea bona, ba tla phela kahar’a Lirapa le nyakallo"
  52,18,"Ba thabisitsoe ke tseo Mong`a bona aba sitsitseng ka tsona, Mong`a bona U tla ba lopolla Kotlong ea Mollo"
  52,19,"(Ho tla thoe ho bona:) “le je le noe, ka phaello le bophelo ka lebaka la liketso tsa lona.”"
  52,20,Ba tla phomola holim’a Literone tse hlophisitsoeng ka mekhahlelo. Re tla ba nyalisa basali ba mahlo a nchocho a khahlang
  52,21,"Bohle Ba-Kholoang, ba bile ba setsoe morao ke malapa a bona Tumelong, Re tla ba matahants’a le malapa a bona, ha Re ke ke Ra fokotsa meputso ea liketso tsa bona. Motho e mong le e mong ke paki liketsong tsa hae"
  52,22,"Re tla ba sitsa ka litholoana le nama, tsohle tseo ba li thabelang"
  52,23,"Kamoo, ba tla neheletsana senoelo se hloekileng malebana le ts’ila efe, se senang koli"